Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.98,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　私は私だから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.31,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これでいいってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もしかして　生徒Aって何か設定ある子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.05,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ある子です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,マジですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:04.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,連載では描いてないんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:11.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そっか　この表情はそれか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もういっぺん　今のとこ聞けますか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.02,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　流します
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,またね　ツバキ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.34,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,陽菜　自分なんかやっちゃったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,たぶん私じゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:31.44,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それか2人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.89,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　私は私だから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.75,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なるほどね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:42.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,この2人には連載で語られてない接点があったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:43.74,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.37,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ツバキはこの子と知り合うことで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ブルームボールの魅力に目覚めて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:52.78,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あと　実はツバキの理論家の設定も　ある意味…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,すいません　こちらの説明不足で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.86,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私がもうちょっと原作から読み取ってればよかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.62,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,こっちのミスですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,申し訳ない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.11,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私全然こだわってなかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さっきまで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.72,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ああ　今ので
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.01,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　今ので
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありますよね　そういうの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:19.97,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あります
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それで　これでオッケーってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:23.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いえ　録り直しましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.29,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,録るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.17,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.37,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう一度ちゃんと　いいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.40,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,お任せします
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,カット18からのツバキと生徒A
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.37,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ひゃい　すすす…　すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,演技やり過ぎちゃいました？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや　やり過ぎてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.22,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,その方向で正解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.23,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,正解？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:47.92,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,監督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ツバキと生徒A
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さっきの感じで　もっと気持ち込めていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,尺は気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.51,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あとからこっちで合わすから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.71,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さっきの感じ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.21,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もっと気持ち込めて…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.50,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,分かった？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.50,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:06.67,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,このシーンのカット　俺に回しといて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:07.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.88,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,カット18から
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:12.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,テイク2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.61,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,またね　ツバキ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.21,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ツバキなら　あっちでも絶対…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:31.78,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.86,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　私は私だから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.66,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　オーケーです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.54,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,頂きます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:53.99,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,舞花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:54.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:55.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,戻ってカット13からのアヤメ　別録り
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう心配させないでよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:12.34,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でも　2人の演技はとってもよかったと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.91,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,声優っていいな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:17.50,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:19.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい　オーケーです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,以上でAパート終わりです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.23,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,お疲れさまです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ねえ　早かった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.93,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,アフレコって疲れるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私もヘロヘロ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.83,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,陽菜　それ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.29,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,台本がヘロヘロ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:50.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.34,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,うん　最高に楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:06.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ここが私の　夢見た場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.69,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ケイちゃん　思い出したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.91,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もともと忘れてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:12.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:15.02,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,名前　なんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:19.75,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,モモミ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,梅ノ木モモミ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:59.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,次回　「向かい風を捕まえて」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue Chinese
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.09,0:00:04.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.68,0:00:10.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,大家喜欢就好
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,饭后的茶来了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是焙茶吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,宿舍生活也渐渐习惯了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.69,0:00:21.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,虽然房间有点小
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,只是你添置了太多健身用品吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,全都是我需要的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我反而觉得床比较碍事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你要睡在哪里啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.02,0:00:38.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真是的 我光是因为单人房间就感动得不行了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我喜欢和室
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,榻榻米上要有被炉
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.50,0:00:46.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我一定得是木地板
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.77,0:00:50.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,舞花 怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在说自己的房间
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.65,0:00:57.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你住习惯了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.91,0:00:59.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,已经习惯啦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.13,0:01:01.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.67,0:01:02.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什么差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有人回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.19,0:01:09.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,欢… 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要吃晚饭吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.94,0:01:17.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们买了便当
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.50,0:01:22.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,别 睡在这里会感冒的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,回房间吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没… 没事吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.23,0:01:37.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.54,0:01:41.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,最近每天都这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,说明训练课很严格吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们也来练习吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.41,0:01:52.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也对 距离正式录音只剩两天了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.67,0:01:53.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没有异议
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.90,0:01:54.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜也来…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.23,0:01:55.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 你回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么突然出门了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,去便利店买了点东西
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要一起练习吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我先回趟房间
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,咦 你还买了卷心菜啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,突然想吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就这样整颗吃吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,而且还是在房间？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一个人吃？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是… 是的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,最近蔬菜摄入不足
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你在隐瞒什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没有隐瞒呀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.68,0:04:22.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,先… 先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么样 要去确认吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,能听到说话声
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是在打电话吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来 啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今天也吃了好多 我好欣慰
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是电话吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,门没锁
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 我们进来了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候来的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你背后是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有什么吗 没有哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那该不会是…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.89,0:05:13.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不要叫他乌龟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,抱… 抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不对 这就是乌龟吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问是乌龟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,大家也不喜欢自己被称作人类吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.31,0:05:28.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,他有自己的名字 叫龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对 龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,长得很有沧桑感吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟不都长这样
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都说了不是乌龟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,话说 阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.46,0:05:45.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,宿舍不允许养宠物哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.09,0:05:49.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这么一说 搬进来的时候莉央说过
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你应该是知道的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是 龟井先生是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我有什么烦恼的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就会找龟井先生商量
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉跟他可以无话不说
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你看 他长得就很像哲学家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,乌龟都长一个样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是确实是违反规定了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没有龟井先生的话 我就不知所措了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我们如果同意的话
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以允许龟井先生住进来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么这么说 穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.91,0:06:43.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我家里也有养狗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,陪我一起长大的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是 穗乃香离开了狗狗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,应该很想念和它一起的生活吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟狗实在不好带过来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过 我懂那种难舍难分的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,而且龟井先生也不会叫
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们四个人决定吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们出演同一部作品
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,宿舍房间也比较靠近
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也算是一个团队了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然前提是不能给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你们四个商量决定就好
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们四个…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来决定
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.10,0:07:28.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我没关系 同意
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.62,0:07:31.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这位蟹江先生 他凶猛吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是蟹江先生啦 是龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不凶猛哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那我也同意
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要跟宿舍里其他人 还有之后要搬进来的人确认
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,记住了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.34,0:07:50.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,鹤田先生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是龟井先生
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,龟井先生 你怎么想
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以进来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,总感觉睡不着
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟明天就要正式录音了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,而且还有超有名的声优一起
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.83,0:08:37.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,光是考虑怎么打招呼 就让人操心
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,志穗和穗乃香呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,已经睡着了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,羡慕她们的从容啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为明天练习呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我的角色虽然是无名配角
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但我还是想尽全力
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以和龟井先生商量了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,他听我说了很多
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 来一起练习吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以吗 舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,反正也睡不着
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,总感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这里椿的心情让我有些在意
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,椿的表情真不错啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这个表情应该配合什么样的演技呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么样 合适吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.32,0:10:01.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但是我有点喜欢你刚才的椿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.29,0:10:03.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.46,0:10:09.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要是学生A的表情也画出来了就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.89,0:10:14.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过你看 她能让椿露出这样的表情
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以再练一遍吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要记住哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这就是录音第一天的气氛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谁来着
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原作者和编辑
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那么 出演的四个人去打招呼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,首先记得说明自己的角色和名字
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,打扰了 我们是AiRBLUE
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.17,0:11:00.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是饰演绯车椿的鹰取舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 有劳了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是饰演凛堂天城的鹿野志穗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是饰演菖蒲彩芽的月居穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.32,0:11:28.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那个 我… 我是六石阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是经纪人五十铃
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.95,0:11:36.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.90,0:11:40.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还有 我带来了三个人观摩学习
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,听说了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请坐在入口旁边的沙发
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,打招呼可真好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有一种真正的声优的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是真的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.88,0:12:04.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,首先有请原作者 无量坂京子老师
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,小京 打招呼了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请… 请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来开始测试
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在遥远未来的世界某处
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.61,0:12:42.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这是为一颗球赌上全部青春的少女们的故事
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,决定全国花球头号队伍的大赛上
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,现在被视为冠军最有力争夺者的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是圣天蓝学园
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.25,0:12:59.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,火花不过是个常规选手名录上都没有的新人
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,根本算不上我的对手
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,激热从去年起成员就没变过啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,战斗力100%解析完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今年当然也是圣天蓝夺冠
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟 我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,社团人数不够
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这样都没法参加大赛了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,A Part 测试完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,刚才是测试
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.88,0:13:57.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,测试？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.99,0:14:02.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,监督会和大家讨论刚才的测试
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后会提出变更和指令
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,加入这些变化后 再正式录音
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道在说什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真好奇
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来从头开始
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,首先是13卡的天城
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,志穗 提到天城了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「百分之百」的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「Percent」的「Per」稍微加重一些
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,百分之百？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.33,0:14:37.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,天城之后也都这样
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,14卡的彩芽
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,单独录音
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,单独录音…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.18,0:14:48.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是主线的时候不录吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后是之后的六花
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,单独录音？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.82,0:14:59.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,主线？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,训练课还没有提到吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是紧接着的台词有重叠的部分
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.37,0:15:09.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,录音的时候就分为主线和单独录音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也就是说穗乃香的部分之后录？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.21,0:15:12.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,主线录完之后 在单独录音的时候录
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后 最后要有居高临下的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是 谢谢指导
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后 我看看…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,35卡之后的火花
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.46,Dial-CH2,,0,0,0,,演技要更加强硬一些
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没问题啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,该庆幸吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.93,0:15:34.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来正式录音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,正式录音开始
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.80,0:16:02.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,火花不过是个常规选手名录上都没有的新人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,根本算不上我的对手
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.14,0:16:08.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,激热从去年起成员就没变过啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,战斗力100%解析完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.87,0:16:16.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今年当然也是圣天蓝夺冠
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,社团人数不够
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这样都没法参加大赛了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好的 主线收录完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.93,0:17:07.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我看看 18卡开始的学生A和椿
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哦 那两个人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是不是有点感情投入过多
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 就那样… 那样就好
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.71,0:17:17.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那样就好
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.70,0:17:19.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,小京
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,18卡开始的椿和学生A
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再播放一次
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.06,0:17:43.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这样就好吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.52,0:18:00.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,难道说 学生A也是有设定的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是有的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.07,0:18:04.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过连载中没有画
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.62,0:18:11.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对哦 这表情是这个意思
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,能再听一遍刚才的部分吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是 这就播放
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 是不是我搞砸了呀
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉会不会是我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.68,0:18:31.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还是我们两个
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟 我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.06,0:18:42.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这两个人之间 有着连载中没有讲述的故事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.03,0:18:43.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,椿是因为认识了她
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,才明白了花球的魅力
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.95,0:18:52.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还有 椿理论家的设定 一定意义上也是…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思 是我们说明不足
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要是能多解读一下原作就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是我的失误
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我之前完全没有注意
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,直到刚才
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊 通过刚才的表演
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 刚才的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有时候就是这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.18,0:19:19.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以 这样就OK了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.30,0:19:23.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 重录一遍吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要录吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再好好录一次 可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,18卡开始的椿和学生A
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是 对对对… 对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是我们演得太夸张了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 并不夸张
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这个方向是正确的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,正确？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.23,0:19:47.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,监督
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,椿和学生A
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就按刚才的感觉 再多投入一些感情
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不用在意分镜
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,之后我们会配合调整
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,刚才的感觉？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,多投入感情…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.35,0:20:06.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这一幕的卡 再给我过一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.96,0:20:07.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,18卡开始
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.03,0:20:12.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,第二次
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再见了 椿
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以你的实力 在那边…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也绝对没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.02,0:20:31.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好了 OK
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,录好了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.95,0:20:53.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,舞花
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.13,0:20:54.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.19,0:20:55.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,回到13卡开始的彩芽 单独录音
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不要让我们担心啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.72,0:21:12.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过 她们两个演得非常好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,声优真好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.41,0:21:17.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.71,0:21:19.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好了 OK
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,A Part 到此结束
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是啊 好快
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,录音还挺累的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我也累得软绵绵了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,阳菜 你的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,台本软绵绵了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.29,0:21:50.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 太开心了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.43,0:22:06.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这里就是 我梦想的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,小京 你想起来了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,本来也没忘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.14,0:22:12.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.53,0:22:15.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.89,0:22:19.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,桃实
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,梅之木桃实
Dialogue: 1,0:23:57.09,0:23:59.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,下集 「捕捉迎面风」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,OP “スタートライン”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:16.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,全ては必然だった　このドアの向こうは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:21.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,あの日見てた夢がほら　語りかける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:26.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,思うように出来なくて　笑ったり泣いたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:32.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,それでも花が咲いたのは　君がいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:37.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,空高く飛ぶ鳥に憧れた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:43.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,届かないものだからって思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:48.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見上げる青空が眩しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,目もくらむほど　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,手を伸ばすほど　高く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:03:00.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,どこまでも飛んでいけるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:06.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,今始まるここがスタートライン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:11.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ここにいる自分を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:17.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,聴こえるだろう　本当の心は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,いつでもその声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:27.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}背中を押してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:16.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,在这扇门的背后 一切都是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:21.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你看那曾经的梦想 正要与你对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:26.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,有些事不能如愿 时而欢笑时而流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:32.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,但花朵依然盛开 是因为身边有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:37.85,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,展翅高飞的鸟儿让人憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:43.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,因为那是无法触及的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:48.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,碧蓝的天空是那么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,向着令人目眩的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,向着触手可及的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:03:00.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不论哪里都可以飞得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:06.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,这里就是我们的起点线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:11.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,要相信站在这里的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:17.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你听得到自己的真心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,总是相信着你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,那信赖的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:27.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}会永远助你前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ED “はじまりの鐘の音が鳴り響く空”
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.58,0:22:35.04,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}I’ll always believe tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.97,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}瞳の奥に映し出す夢が
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.97,0:22:49.35,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}前へと進む理由をくれた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.35,0:22:54.65,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}この手に　たくさんの意味をのせて
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.10,0:22:58.65,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}忘れかけてた　絆には気づかない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.65,0:23:02.15,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}歩む景色は　霞んで消えてく
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.11,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}Until you can’t see it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.37,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}どんなに汚れたって
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.37,0:23:14.12,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}おもちゃ箱に全部詰め込んでいた夢には
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.13,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}言葉にはない　形にもない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.88,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}ここにしか無い君がいるから
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.88,0:23:25.89,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}はじまりの鐘の音が
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.89,0:23:30.01,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}鳴り響く空　雲をかき分け　ほら
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.56,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}世界を包んでいく
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.56,0:23:38.82,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}踏み出す勇気抱きしめて
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.82,0:23:41.19,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}届いていて　今
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.19,0:23:46.07,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}瞳に　映るこの奇跡には
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.07,0:23:51.08,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,夢のはじまりの合図が鳴る
Comment: 1,0:22:31.58,0:22:35.04,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}I’ll always believe tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.97,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}映照在目光深处的梦想
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.97,0:22:49.35,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}给了我前行的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.35,0:22:54.65,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}将各种意义  托付在这只手中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.10,0:22:58.65,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}未曾注意到  几乎被忘记的情谊
